{"tid":1668733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 為三跑繞過立法會 設立機場建設費 每名旅客徵收每程$90至$180元","createTime":"2019-10-22T07:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:47:13.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8652506e233debc6e8b9660e92592de009261ddb","tid":1668733,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">波叔好野,乾坤大挪移</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場建設費料徵至2030年<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為興建機場三跑道，機管局去年八月起向旅客徵收機場建設費，截至今年三月底已徵收款項達十九億元，估計徵費會持續至二○三○年，<span style=\"color: red;\">以每名旅客徵收每程九十至一百八十元不等的機場建設費計算</span>，期內可為三跑籌得二百六十億元。而機管局停止向政府派息十年，將可保留約四百七十億元盈餘。另外，機管局計劃為三跑向市場發行綠色債券，將集資所得金額用於興建造價達二百六十億元的新客運大樓。"},{"pid":"1040f8c1e5687a554bd8055be5c7c04c92d134e3","tid":1668733,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"$120等於變相俾三跑建設費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74518dd9ab03a800e381921925f6e417dd98572d","tid":1668733,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"好彩窮𨶙唔搭飛機，政府無得係我身上拎Jetso<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50ff0fd7dc7be752dde017289c80ef66da0d0c9","tid":1668733,"uid":45783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"政府又唔可以直接比錢起3跑,又怕無人出境收唔到錢起3跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01732d1c7a5e93e507a107a10c3925d2ee22107","tid":1668733,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50ff0fd7dc7be752dde017289c80ef66da0d0c9","tid":1668733,"uid":45783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"政府又唔可以直接比錢起3跑,又怕無人出境收唔到錢起3跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s